%% BM25 Test Queries with Relevance Judgments
%% Format: [{Query, #{relevant => [DocNums], partial => [DocNums]}}]
%%
%% relevant: Documents that are highly relevant (should appear in top-K)
%% partial: Documents that are somewhat relevant (acceptable in results)
%%
%% DocNums refer to doc1, doc2, etc. (as integers 1-100)

